  "type": "mcq",
  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The table above shows some pairs of <span class=\"italic\">x</span> values and&nbsp;<span class=\"italic\">y</span>&nbsp;values. Which of the following equations could represent the relationship between <span class=\"italic\">x</span> and <span class=\"italic\">y</span> ?</p>\n",
